prompt_text: Describe your stay at a resort.
content_text: I woke up early in the morning to have the chance to see the sunrise. We have a wonderful view to the room. I had a chance to go to the pool. I have a great time on the restaurants. They have a lovely meals and have really accessible places for every people. The customer service people is really, really nice. They're really conscious about what they're doing. Anne provided wonderful support.
